title: U of Mn 3 BR in Vintage Building Close to Campus Available 9/1
posting_body: ['Large 3 BR + office unit on 4th floor of well cared for vintage building close to campus.', '1300 + sq feet.', ' Units have hardwood floors throughout and dishwashers.', 'Lots of storage space.', 'Additional storage in basement for a small fee.', 'Deposit is $1850, owner pays heat, tenants pay water, trash, electric.', 'Cats ok $25/mo pet fee.', 'Rental Criteria 6/1/2020', '-verifiable income equivalent to 2.75 times rent.', 'Example: if rent is $900 you must show income of $900 x 2.75 or $2,475/mo.', 'At least 2 check stubs required as verification.', '-positive ownership or rental history.', 'We need a reference from current and past landlords or property management companies.', '-any negative credit or bank references is criteria for denial.', 'This includes poor payment history and/or a bankruptcy filing.', '-any unlawful detainer or eviction actions within the last 3 years', '-no misdemeanor convictions within 3 years, no felony offenses within 7 years']
